sequenceDiagram
    actor R as Requestor
    participant FG as /front-gate
    participant KB as Knowledge Base
    participant FS as docs/requests/

    R->>FG: /front-gate "idea"

    note over FG: Phase 1 — Interpret & Orient
    FG->>R: Restate idea in plain language. Correct?
    R->>FG: Confirmed / corrected
    FG->>KB: Check ~/.claude/knowledge/systems/ for named systems (silent)
    KB-->>FG: Constraints noted — carried into Phase 2

    note over FG: Phase 2 — Grill (one question at a time)
    loop Q1–Q7
        FG->>R: Question + plain-language example answer
        alt System named in answer
            FG->>R: ⚠️ Constraint on [system] — note in brief?
            R->>FG: Acknowledged
        end
        R->>FG: Answer
    end

    note over FG: Phase 3 — Draft Brief
    FG->>FG: Compile answers into Request Brief (FORMATS.md)

    note over FG: Phase 4 — Review
    FG->>R: Present full draft. (yes / edit / cancel)
    alt edit
        R->>FG: Revise section X
        FG->>R: Re-present updated draft
    else cancel
        FG->>R: Brief discarded (brief was wrong)
    end
    R->>FG: yes

    note over FG: Phase 5 — Submission
    FG->>R: Submit to Jira / Save as draft / Discard?
    alt [1] Submit to Jira
        FG->>FS: Save brief (status: pending-jira)
        FG->>R: ✅ Flagged for Jira submission — company integration will raise ticket
    else [2] Save as draft
        FG->>FS: Save brief (status: draft)
        FG->>R: ✅ Saved — team runs /idea to explore feasibility
    else [3] Discard
        FG->>R: Brief discarded (changed mind)
    end
